        <div class="content-body">
          <p>Obtaining a student visa is often the most stressful part of the study abroad process. Grant Consulting provides complete visa application support, guiding students through the specific requirements of each country's embassy or consulate. Whether you are applying for a US F-1 visa, a UK Tier 4 visa, a Schengen student visa, or any other type, our team ensures your application is thorough, accurate, and submitted on time.</p>
          <p>Document preparation is where most visa applications succeed or fail. We help you compile and organize every required document — acceptance letters, financial statements, bank guarantees, insurance certificates, and sponsorship letters — and review each one to make sure it meets the exact specifications set by the embassy. Our attention to detail significantly reduces the risk of delays or rejections.</p>
          <p>Many student visas require an in-person or online interview at the embassy. We prepare you with mock interview sessions that cover the most commonly asked questions, help you articulate your study plans and intentions clearly, and build your confidence so you can present yourself professionally. After submission, we continue to track your application status and advise you on any follow-up steps required.</p>
        </div>

